\s1 Paul told the soldiers he was a Roman, so they didn’t whip him
\p 
\v 23 \w The|strong="G2532"\w* mob \w kept|strong="G2532"\w* \w on|strong="G1519"\w* \w shouting|strong="G2905"\w*, “Kill \w him|strong="G3588"\w*.” \w And|strong="G2532"\w* \w they|strong="G2532"\w* \w took|strong="G2532"\w* \w off|strong="G4495"\w* \w their|strong="G2532"\w* \w coats|strong="G2440"\w*, \w and|strong="G2532"\w* \w they|strong="G2532"\w* \w threw|strong="G4496"\w* dirt \w into|strong="G1519"\w* \w the|strong="G2532"\w* air, \w to|strong="G1519"\w* show \w that|strong="G3588"\w* \w they|strong="G2532"\w* \w were|strong="G3588"\w* \w very|strong="G2532"\w* angry.
